crm_notes.title: Rosanna Paknoush — Research Profile
crm_notes.body: Rosanna Paknoush is a Family Nurse Practitioner with over 9 years of diverse clinical experience, having graduated from Pace University in 2017 with a specialization in Family Practice Nursing. She holds active nursing licenses in 16 states and serves as a provider for Valhalla Vitality's integrative health and wellness telehealth platform, while also maintaining her practice at Geriatric Medical Care Inc since May 2018. She is affiliated with medical groups including Ion Oltean Physician Pc and Upstate Geriatric Medical Services Pc, and operates from her office in Forest Hills, Queens.

crm_notes.title: Cielo Quiambao — Research Profile
crm_notes.body: Maria Regina 'Ciel' Quiambao is a Certified Public Accountant (CPA) and Real Estate Broker (REB) with over ten years of experience in finance and accounting. She currently serves as Senior Finance Business Partner at Max's Group Inc., the largest casual dining restaurant company in the Philippines. Previously, she worked at PwC and Ramcar Batteries Inc. She is also a digital creator and fitness coach with a social media presence focused on health and wellness content.
